Package de.unpixelt.locale

Class Translate

  • java.lang.Object
    • org.bukkit.plugin.PluginBase
      • org.bukkit.plugin.java.JavaPlugin
        • de.unpixelt.locale.Translate
  • All Implemented Interfaces:
    CommandExecutor, TabCompleter, TabExecutor, Plugin
    public final class Translate
extends JavaPlugin
    With Translate you can translate
    • Biomes
    • Materials
    • Potions
    • PotionEffects
    • Enchantments
    • Entities
    • TropicalFishes
    • Villager
    with the giving Locale or Player(uses getLocale(Player))

    When a translation is requested the specific Locale is cached for two minutes. If in that two minutes no further requests are taken it will be automatically cleared from the cache.
